title: Rocky Mountain Gastroenterology Settlement Ends Class Action Lawsuit Over Sept. 2024 Data Breach
description: A Rocky Mountain Gastroenterology settlement offers cash and credit monitoring to victims of a Sept. 2024 data breach.

title: $1M Dakota Eye Institute Settlement Ends Class Action Lawsuit Over October 2023 Data Breach
description: A $1M Dakota Eye Institute class action settlement offering cash and credit monitoring wraps up litigation over an October 2023 data breach.

title: $700M Google Settlement Ends Attorneys General Lawsuit Over Alleged Monopoly of Android App Distribution
description: A $700M Google settlement ends an attorneys general lawsuit that alleged the tech giant monopolized app distribution and in-app billing for Android mobile devices.

title: $625K Hypertension Nephrology Associates Settlement Ends Class Action Over January 2024 Data Breach
description: Hypertension Nephrology Associates has agreed to a $625K class action settlement to resolve a lawsuit over a January 2024 data breach.

title: $1.1M Oklahoma Spine Hospital Settlement Ends Class Action Suit Over July 2024 Data Breach
description: A $1.1M Oklahoma Spine Hospital class action settlement offers cash and credit monitoring to individuals affected by a July 2024 data breach.

title: $5M Papa John’s Class Action Settlement Ends ‘No Poach’ Employee Antitrust Litigation
description: A $5M Papa John’s settlement offers cash to current and former Papa John’s employees between 2014 and 2021.

title: $1M M&D Capital Premier Billing Settlement Ends Litigation Over 2023 Data Breach
description: M&D Capital Premier Billing will pay $1M to resolve a class action lawsuit over a data breach discovered in July 2023.

title: $500K Asheville Arthritis Settlement Ends Class Action Lawsuit Over May 2024 Data Breach
description: A $500K Asheville Arthritis and Osteoporosis Center settlement offers cash to consumers whose info may have been involved in a May 2024 data breach.

title: $7.75M Purpose Financial Settlement Ends Class Action Lawsuit Over February 2023 Data Breach
description: A $7.75M Purpose Financial class action settlement offers cash to consumers whose information was potentially exposed in a February 2023 data breach.

title: $3.25M Lemonaid Health Settlement Ends Pixel Data Sharing Class Action Lawsuit
description: A $3.25M Lemonaid Health settlement resolves a class action lawsuit over tracking pixels that allegedly transmitted personal data to third parties.

title: $1.4M Nationwide Settlement Resolves Class Action Over Allegedly Unsolicited Pet Insurance Voice Messages
description: Nationwide Mutual Insurance Co. has agreed to a $1.4M settlement to resolve a class action suit over allegedly unsolicited prerecorded voice messages.

title: $800K Interim Healthcare Settlement Ends Data Breach Class Action Lawsuit
description: Interim Healthcare of Lubbock, Texas, is set to pay $800,000 to settle a class action lawsuit over a 2022 data breach.

title: Up to $18M Rayus Radiology Settlement Ends Class Action Lawsuit Over Alleged Data Sharing
description: An $18M Rayus Radiology settlement offers cash and privacy protection to current and former patient portal accountholders.
